Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's coming!\N-Grab onto something!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.93,0:00:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... it's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being pulled!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the bridge\Nto get it closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.49,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it until it's 10 meters close!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.25,0:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.22,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Bring the bullets over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.64,0:00:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomb lance, ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hides behind the clouds again\Nit's going to be troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.68,0:01:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes too wild,\Nthe meat's taste will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going on his own again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.05,0:02:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was quite scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mika finished it!\N-Lower the hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get moving it's gonna sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Takita,\Ndon't stay there astonished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.11,0:02:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... dragon hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.74,0:02:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jumping onto a dragon that still\Nhad some strength left is too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate bomb lances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Chasing dragons that swim through the sky,\NTo the west, east, south and north.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:03:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, there aren't much left.\NDraking vessel on service: Quin Zaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dissecting the dragons they capture,\Nand selling them during their travels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have a port to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching the wind, seizing the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,their journey goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The hoist machine is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have many wounds too, nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna sell for quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ship sure is full of holes though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't get so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what do they think a ship is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Get number 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful with that\Nso it doesn't get any scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for large trading auctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Retail is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! How much do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Fill me this with oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our oil is extracted from the skin\Nright after we capture it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it for cooking too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-And today's smells especially well!\N-Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How about some meat too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't eat it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you can pickle it in salt or smoke it\Nand it will last for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I will take some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, don't you think you're\Nbetter suited for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But with just this, I won't be able\Nto get into the ship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have dragon liver?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it works for night blindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Mika-san, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Skipping out and snitching foo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not snitching food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just scraping the meet that was\Nstuck on the bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be a waste, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Chop logic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wha?\N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, fresh dragon meat\Ntastes good even raw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go snithing food when you're just a newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not it, it's just that Mika-san...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Aaah, I'm so so busy...\N-Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miiiikaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,60% for us. Nothing less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not satisfied then this deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's also a limit to the amount of\Nbooze we can put on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only thing I envy from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, it's always you\Nwho's doing whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, don't learn anything from him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No roof for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe there isn't a single room avaliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't the women at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been on the ship for a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted the crew to get a good rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the townspeople are scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what they say, when a draking vessel\Nstops in a town, a dragon will fall on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How ill omened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a superstition!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Jiro.\N-It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Draking vessels go around places\Nwhere dragons appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely because we take down dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can prevent damage before it happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need your pretentious talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't even registered in the association,\Njust an unlicensed ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't trust you all the more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't really welcome here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We're strangers no matter where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're letting you do business here\Nwithout kicking you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that more than enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry for imposing on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're more than used to living in the ship,\Nso don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you the necessary supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're done you better get out of here quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anything, Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say we are respectable even as flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll buy the meat and oil of the dragon we captured
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but they won't let us into the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not reasonable, any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I hoped I could sleep\Nsprawled for once...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take a bath too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, what, Mika-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you pretend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wondered if you smelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, you can sleep anywhere as long\Nas you have a pillow, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't made as sturdy as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A-and then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I... smelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... you smelled like a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you start a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I got hungry after work, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A grill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as there's straw and charcoal,\Nopen fire is good too,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is pine for the oil mill\Nand it has a lot of resin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, judging from how it tasted raw,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be really good as steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san always looks absent-minded,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but when it comes to food\Nhe gets really talkative.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Creepy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Slice this rock-hard bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Spread the dragon's fat on the iron plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's done on both sides,\Na splash of grappa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Slice the steak and put it between bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hm?\N-Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're monopolizing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's big enough to share it with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! Give me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,For me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat that much now\Nyou won't be able to eat dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I helped you start the fire, give me my share!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Exactly!\N-My share!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Heeeey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon... a dragon appeared\Nabove the neighbour town! I just got a call!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There were more aside from that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what a bummer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's your job, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go exterminate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you tell us to go now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We just finished dissecting one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and we haven't refueled either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry that much,\Nthey rarely attack people directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not like the dragon\Nwill fall on the town for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife and daughter are in that town!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late after it happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you hunters are for!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only saying what's convenient for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika! We haven't even refueled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the neighbouring town, right?\NWe don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go, capture it, and come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a dragon, we have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko, put out the fire of the oiling pot\Nand put on a lid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Go tell the bridge\Nto get ready for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're turning it on soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shall we?\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro and Vannie go call those who are resting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, time to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking that we gotta sleep\Nin a small cabin after getting back...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really worth it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of... of course we'll prepare a place\Nto sleep, a bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Food and drink too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get everyone,\Nwe're untying the mooring line!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the cargo on the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how is it this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly above the town of all things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bigger than the one we got this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Something is off...\Nthe atmosphere feels tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gibbs, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how it's rising its plumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's calling its friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to dragons,\Nwhat he says is never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there are more around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, it's not reacting to flash bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It better not be doing it on purpose\Nknowing we can't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything if it's above the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If another one shows up we're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mika!\NWhat are you gonna do if it starts rampaging?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll think about that when it happens.\N-Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For now... we don't have to worry about\Nthe town anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it suddenly got aggresive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if it was angry with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,bring as many bomb lances as you find!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"It looks angry" you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells the same as the one\Nwe took down today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably, this one's the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it noticed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's angry because we ate her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the one it was calling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I know this is being too soft but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit bad for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you misunderstanding\Nwhat hunters are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons aren't something\Nthat just wait to be hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are not ready to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,-Crocco-san!\N-Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's not going to last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have it rampaging over the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cute the anchor's rope\Nand shake it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.85,0:16:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to reposition ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we can't be sure\Nit won't go back to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If the ship sinks it\Nwill all be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you save me a bit more gently...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This one'll be hanging on for dear life\Nuntil it runs out of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't possibly shake it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll finish it as is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How many bullets did we shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this thing feel any pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really feel any reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita! Bring me a stun lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Y... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use that, the taste gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna bring it down, we gotta do it\Nas delicious as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You think this is the moment to say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, cover me with a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll go too!\N-Ah- hey, Jiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna eat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocco-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you do, but raise the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-Don't let it go, Jiro!\N-The hook, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stun lance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up using it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When was the last time we ate such a feast?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-One more bottle, please.\N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie, don't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have opened 3 bottles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's the last, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't eat more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bliss...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, so sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These days
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we only had salted meat stew to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not saying your cooking is bad,\NYoshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Mika, since I had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed the restaurant's kitchen\Nand roasted it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You used a stun lance, right?\NI wonder how's the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With dragons, you don't know until you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good...\N-Yeah, you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Takita, you're a newbie,\NI don't want to see you yawning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't control a yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a morning person...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're like that,\Nyou're gonna let dragons escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragons are early to bed early to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since countries started to aim for the sky\Npursuing the rare dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it's been about half a century.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, there aren't much left.\NDraking vessel on service: Quin Zaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursuing their meat, oil and entrails,\Nand sometimes the bounty they have on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chasing the dragons that swim through the sky and air.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have a port to go home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Catching the wind, seizing the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,their journey goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
